</paragraph>
<paragraph id="CF691F589052B5200D15808AAF5DB0CD" pageId="24" pageNumber="119">
<normalizedToken id="9B3B9D1E80B1E08345FB2B6EE5AA3986" originalValue="QUÉBEC">QUEBEC</normalizedToken>
: 
<normalizedToken id="7B8435C5F934858E54B6275B6C7B2158" originalValue="Châteauguay">Chateauguay</normalizedToken>
Co., Ormstown, 12.VII.1977, sweeping, E. J. Kiteley [1♀, CNC]; same data, except 30.VII.1978 [1♂, CNC]; Huntingdon Co., Covey Hill, 30.VI.1927, G. S. Walley [1♀, CNC]; same data, except 1.VII.1927, W. J. Brown [1♀, CNC].
